flowchart TD
    User[User / Admin] --> Portal[AWS Access Portal]
    Portal --> Management[Management Account]
    Portal --> Sandbox[Sandbox Account]
    Portal --> Network[Network Account]

    Management --> Organizations[AWS Organizations]
    Organizations --> OUs[Organizational Units]
    Organizations --> SCPs[Service Control Policies]

    SCPs --> SandboxOU[Sandbox OU]
    SandboxOU --> Sandbox

    Network --> AssumeRole[STS AssumeRole]
    AssumeRole --> SandboxRole[SandboxEC2ReadOnlyRole]
    SandboxRole --> EC2ReadOnly[EC2 Read-Only Access]

    Repo[GitHub Repository] --> Actions[GitHub Actions Terraform CI]
    Actions --> ValidateMgmt[Validate Management]
    Actions --> ValidateSandbox[Validate Sandbox]

    Terraform[Terraform Code] --> Management
    Terraform --> Sandbox
